HEADWORD: Encenia
<hw>En*ce"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>encaenia</ets>, fr. Gr. <?/ a feast of dedication; <?/ in + <?/
new.]</ety> <def>A festival commemorative of the founding of a city or
